## Note: lines beginning with '#' are comments
## Mapping from the morph-it lexicon to ciapetti's tagset for 
## Apache OpenNLP. File is in *TAB* separated value format.

## Note that these tags are all prefixes of the actual tags used by
## Morph-it and the OpenNLP PoS tagger.

## First column: morph-it tag
## Second column: OpenNLP tag
## Third column: explanation 

